-5415.2008.01705.x</pub-id><pub-id pub-id-type="pmid">18410323</pub-id></element-citation></ref><ref id="CR9"><label>9.</label><element-citation publication-type="book"><person-group person-group-type="author"><collab>National Institute for Health and Care Excellence &#x00026; Social Care Institute for Excellence (NICE/SCIE)</collab></person-group><source>Dementia: supporting people with dementia and their carers in health and social care. National Clinical Practice Guideline Number CG 042</source><year>2006</year><publisher-loc>London</publisher-loc><publisher-name>NICE</publisher-name></element-citation></ref><ref id="CR10"><label>10.</label><element-citation publication-type="book"><person-group person-group-type="author"><name><surname>Graff</surname><given-names>M</given-names></name><name><surname>Melick</surname><given-names>M</given-names></name><name><surname>Thijssen</surname><given-names>M</given-names></name><name><surname>Verstraten</surname><given-names>P</given-names></name><name><surname>Zajec</surname><given-names>J</given-names></name></person-group><source>Ergotherapie bij ouderen met dementie en hun mantelzorgers: Het EDOMAH-programma</source><year>2010</year><publisher-loc>Houten</publisher-loc><publisher-name>Bohn Stafleu van Loghum</publisher-name></element-citation></ref><ref id="CR11"><label>11.</label><element-citation publication-type="journal"><person-group person-group-type="author"><name><surname>Graff</surname><given-names>M</given-names></name><name><surname>Vernooij-Dassen</surname><given-names>M</given-names></name><name><surname>Thijssen</surname><given-names>M</given-names></name><name><surname>Dekker</surname><given-names>J</given-names></name><name><surname>Hoefnagels</surname><given-names>W</given-names></name><name><surname>Olde</surname><given-names>RM</given-names></name></person-group><article-title>Community based occupational therapy for patients with dementia and their care givers: randomised controlled trial</article-ti